nginx-waf (0.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Core module implementation complete
  * Multiple named IP lists with tag support
  * Blacklist and whitelist modes
  * IPv4/IPv6 support with CIDR ranges
  * Per-context configuration (http, server, location)
  * waf_enable_lists and waf_disable_lists directives
  * Enhanced logging with client IP and matched list name
  * Input validation for list/tag names

 -- Rumen Damyanov <contact@rumenx.com>  Thu, 16 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0000

nginx-waf (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * Basic waf on/off directive
  * waf_mode blacklist/whitelist directive
  * waf_log_prefix directive

 -- Rumen Damyanov <contact@rumenx.com>  Fri, 24 Dec 2025 12:00:00 +0000
